query:
SELECT
                id,
                tenant_id,
                license_pool_id,
                entitlement_id,
                priority,
                enabled,
                created_at,
                created_by
            FROM gov_license_entitlement_links
            WHERE tenant_id = $1
              AND ($2::uuid IS NULL OR license_pool_id = $2)
              AND ($3::uuid IS NULL OR entitlement_id = $3)
              AND ($4::boolean IS NULL OR enabled = $4)
            ORDER BY priority ASC, created_at DESC
            LIMIT $5 OFFSET $6
